<HEAD><TITLE>Water Quality- Chapter 2-Page 7</TITLE></HEAD>
<BODY BGCOLOR=#86FFEB>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="line.gif" ALT="Line" WIDTH="100%"></CENTER>
<center>
<p>
<A HREF="TXENVALMANAC.HTML">Almanac Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="QUALITYCH2P1.HTML#TABLE">Chapter Two Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="http://WWW.TEC.ORG">TEC Home Page</A>
