<HEAD><TITLE>Public Lands - Chapter 3 - Page 5</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR=#CCFFCC> 

<CENTER><IMG SRC="../line.gif" ALT="Line" WIDTH="100%"></CENTER>
<center>
<p>
<A HREF="../TXENVALMANAC.HTML">Almanac Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="LANDCH3P1.HTML#TABLE">Chapter Three Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="http://WWW.TEC.ORG">TEC Home Page</A>
