<A HREF="NOTES3.HTML">NEXT PAGE</A>* <A HREF="LANDCH3P4.HTML">PREVIOUS PAGE</A>  Go to page 
<A HREF="LANDCH3P1.HTML">1</A>*<A HREF="LANDCH3P2.HTML">2</A>*<A 
HREF="LANDCH3P3.HTML">3</A>*<A HREF="LANDCH3P4.HTML">4</A>*<A 
HREF="LANDCH3P5.HTML">5</A>*<A 
HREF="NOTES3.HTML">Notes</A><p>
