<HEAD><TITLE>Wildlife - Chapter 4 - Page 5</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR=#CCFFCC> 


<CENTER><IMG SRC="../line.gif" ALT="Line" WIDTH="100%"></CENTER>
<center>
<p>
