<IMG SRC="c.energcons.gif" BORDER=4 ALIGN=middle ALT="Pie Chart of Texas Energy Consumption by Source">
<p>
Source: Department of Energy, State Energy Data Report, 1992
</center>


<P><P><P>


<center>
