	<LI><A NAME="36">Lower</A> Colorado River Authority, "LCRA Water Quality Assessment Identifies Priority Problems in Colorado River Watershed," Press Release, October 7, 1994, 4. The 1994 report by the LCRA recommends that the Railroad Commission find additional funding to find and plug abandoned wells. 
