</TD></TR><TR><TD>
Insecticides:</TD><TD ALIGN="RIGHT">8,459,603 lbs.
</TD></TR><TR><TD>
Fungicides:</TD><TD ALIGN="RIGHT">1,658,962 lbs.
</TD></TR><TR><TD>
</TD><TH>POUNDS OF ACTIVE INGREDIENT</TH><TH>ACRES TREATED
