<p>
<A HREF="../TXENVALMANAC.HTML">Almanac Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="PESTICIDESP1.HTML#TABLE">Pesticides Table of Contents</A> | <A HREF="http://WWW.TEC.ORG">TEC Home Page</A>
