<A HREF="philos.html">Bioregionalism |
<A HREF="extra.html">Buy/Grow Local</A> |  
<A HREF="locate.html">Eco-Location</A> | 
<A HREF="texasbio.html">Bioregions of TX</A> |
<A HREF="sprocket.html">Sprockets</A> |
<A HREF="net.html">The Net</A> |  
<A HREF="../index.html">Archive</A>
</CENTER>
</FONT>

<P>

<IMG SRC="images/bgo.gif" WIDTH=456 HEIGHT=3 Alt="Line">
<BR>

<TABLE BORDER="0" WIDTH="456"> <TD VALIGN="TOP" COLSTART="1" WIDTH=65%>
