</FONT></TD>

<TD VALIGN="TOP" COLSTART="2" WIDTH=35% ALIGN="RIGHT"> <IMG WIDTH=126 HEIGHT=51
SRC="images/logo.gif" ALT="T.E.C./AT&T Logos"><P>
</TD></TABLE>

</BODY>

</HTML>
</DOC>
