<P>
</CENTER>
<CENTER><IMG SRC="line.gif" ALT="Line" WIDTH="100%"></CENTER><P>
<H5>Texas Environmental Almanac, Chapter 1, Water Quantity, NOTES, Page 9 </H5>
<H4>
NOTES
