<LI><A NAME="10">It is important to differentiate</A> between water withdrawals versus water consumed. For example, the thermo-electric power generation sector withdraws about 40 to 45 percent of all water in Texas, but consumes only about 3 percent, since most is returned as stream flow. World Resources Institute, <I>The 1994 Information Please Environmental Almanac </I>(Boston: Houghton Mifflin Co., 1994), 272.<P>

