<LI><A NAME="23">Pequod Associates, Inc.</A>, <I>Texas Industrial Water Usage Survey</I> (Pequod Associates, Austin, August 1993). This special survey conducted for the Texas Water Development Board found that the semiconductor industry has reduced their water use by 33 percent over the past few years.<P>

<LI><A NAME="24">Houston &amp</A>; TC Railway v. East 98 Tex 146, 81 SW 279 (1904). This 1904 court case established that groundwater was equivalent to a property right.<P>
 
