<p><H4>Population figures are from 1990.<p>
Source (includes all regional graphs): Texas Water Development Board, Water for Texas 1990: Today and Tomorrow (Austin: TWDB, 1990); and Texas Water Development Board, "Draft Projections of Population and Municipal Water Use," 1996 Consensus Water Plan.</H4>

