<HTML>
<HEAD><TITLE>Air Quality - Chapter 6 - Page 1</TITLE></HEAD> 
<BODY BGCOLOR=#cccccc> 
<CENTER><A HREF="../txenvalmanac.html"><IMG SRC="../tinyalm.gif" ALT="Almanac Icon" BORDER=1> </A>

<H1>Air Quality</H1><H3>CHAPTER SIX</H3>
<H4><I>"Remember when atmospheric contaminants were romantically called stardust?"</I><BR>
Lane Olinghouse</H4></CENTER>
<A NAME="TABLE">*</A>
<CENTER>
<TABLE BORDER=5 WIDTH="85%">
<TR><TD><A HREF="#EVENTS">Events in the Quest for Cleaner Air</A><br>
<B><A HREF="#POLLUTION">What is Air Pollution?</A></B></TD>
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="AIRCH6P1.HTML">Page 1</A></TD></TR>
<TR><TD><A HREF="AIRCH6P2.HTML#CLEAN">The 1990 Federal Clean Air Act</A><BR>
<B><A HREF="AIRCH6P2.HTML#MARKET">Market Incentives in Texas</A><BR></B>
</TD><TD VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="AIRCH6P2.HTML">Page 2</A></td></tr>
<tr><td><A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#NATIONAL">National Ambient Air Quality Standards</A><br>
<OL TYPE=A START=1 >
<LI>  <A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#OZONE">Ozone</A>
<LI>  <A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#SULFUR">Sulfur Dioxide and Nitrogen Oxides - The Building Blocks of Acid Rain</A>
<LI>  <A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#CARBON">Carbon Monoxide</A>
<LI>  <A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#PARTICULATE">Particulate Matter </A> 
<LI>  <A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#LEAD">Lead</A>
</OL>
<B><A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#TREES">Do Trees Pollute?</A></B><BR>
<B><A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML#QUALITY">Air Quality Monitoring: How much do we know?</A></B>
</td>
<TD VALIGN=TOP><A HREF="AIRCH6P3.HTML">Page 3</A></td></tr>
